    "Due to the recent launch of the GPT-4 model within the ChatGPT application, new works are expected to be published soon and will be analyzed as part of future work.",
    "Moreover, as future work, we will study the ethical implications of LLMs (i.e., their transparency and fairness behavior caused by the training data and privacy) and how the solutions discussed can be integrated into the education curricula, as well as their shortcomings and risk to academic integrity (e.g., plagiarism concerns).",
